


Book Management System

-------------------------------------------
Description

A Library where users can login and borrow books from the library.

--------------------------------------------
- /login - post
- this will be for user login where uesr will login and see all sessions.

-/books - get
- this will provide the user with all available books for borrowing

-/borrowed - get
= this will show the user which books they have borrowed

- /getall
- will get all books and arrange them in a template

- /rentbook
- pass id of book to a page to display it in it's full glory

